<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=10"
    />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>DIGITAL TAVERN</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/favicon.png" type="image/png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/background.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/footer.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/FooterPages/Privacy/privacypage.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <div class="app-introduction">
          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p>Learn the rules before adventuring...</p>
        </div>

        <hr class="app-hr" />

        <nav class="app-navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">
          <a href="/"><p>HOME</p></a>
          <a href="/quest"><p>QUEST</p></a>
          <a href="/guild"><p>GUILD</p></a>
          <a href="/blog"><p>BLOG</p></a>
          <a href="/about"><p>ABOUT</p></a>
          <% if (locals.loggedIn) { %>
          <a href="/account"
            ><p id="login-nav-btn"><%= locals.username %></p></a
          >
          <% } else { %>
          <a href="/login"><p id="login-nav-btn">LOGIN</p></a>
          <% } %>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <div class="main-content">
        <main class="policy-content">
          <div class="policy-header">
            <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy Scroll</h1>
            <p class="policy-subtitle">Ancient Laws of Digital Protection</p>
          </div>

          <div class="last-updated">
            <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> June 6th, 2025</p>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
              Introduction to Our Realm
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>
                Welcome, brave adventurer, to The Digital Tavern! This Privacy
                Scroll outlines how we protect your personal information while
                you embark on quests, share your tales, and connect with fellow
                guild members in our realm.
              </p>
              <p>
                By creating a character (account) or using our services, you
                agree to the terms outlined in this sacred document. We are
                committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your
                adventures remain secure.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">üìú</span>
              Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p><strong>Character Information:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Adventurer name (username)</li>
                <li>Email scroll address</li>
                <li>Character level and experience points</li>
                <li>Completed quests and earned badges</li>
                <li>Guild memberships and community participation</li>
              </ul>

              <p><strong>Content You Create:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Blog posts and adventure tales</li>
                <li>Quest submissions and reviews</li>
                <li>Comments and community interactions</li>
                <li>Profile customizations and preferences</li>
              </ul>

              <p><strong>Technical Information:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Device type and browser information</li>
                <li>IP address and location data</li>
                <li>Usage patterns and site interactions</li>
                <li>Cookies and local storage data</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">‚öîÔ∏è</span>
              How We Use Your Information
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>We use your information to enhance your tavern experience:</p>

              <div class="highlight-box">
                <h4>Core Services</h4>
                <p>
                  Managing your character progression, quest completion
                  tracking, and blog publishing capabilities.
                </p>
              </div>

              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Account Management:</strong> Creating and maintaining
                  your adventurer profile
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Content Delivery:</strong> Displaying your blogs,
                  quests, and achievements
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Community Features:</strong> Enabling guild
                  participation and social interactions
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Personalization:</strong> Customizing your experience
                  based on interests and activity
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Communication:</strong> Sending important updates
                  about your account or new features
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Security:</strong> Protecting against fraud, abuse,
                  and unauthorized access
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">üè∞</span>
              Information Sharing & Protection
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>
                <strong>We Never Sell Your Personal Information.</strong> Your
                data is not a commodity to be traded.
              </p>

              <p><strong>Public Information:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Your adventurer name and public profile</li>
                <li>Published blog posts and quest stories</li>
                <li>Community comments and interactions</li>
                <li>Achievement badges and character level</li>
              </ul>

              <p><strong>We may share information only when:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Required by law or legal process</li>
                <li>Necessary to protect user safety or prevent harm</li>
                <li>
                  With service providers who help operate our platform (under
                  strict confidentiality)
                </li>
                <li>In case of business transfer (with notice to users)</li>
              </ul>

              <div class="highlight-box">
                <h4>Data Security Measures</h4>
                <p>
                  We employ industry-standard encryption, secure servers, and
                  regular security audits to protect your information from
                  unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">üóùÔ∏è</span>
              Your Rights & Choices
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>
                As a member of our digital realm, you have the following rights:
              </p>

              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Access:</strong> View all personal information we have
                  about you
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct any inaccurate
                  information
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Deletion:</strong> Request removal of your account and
                  associated data
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Portability:</strong> Export your content and data in
                  a readable format
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Restriction:</strong> Limit how we process certain
                  types of your data
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Objection:</strong> Opt out of certain data processing
                  activities
                </li>
              </ul>

              <p><strong>Account Controls:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Modify privacy settings from your character profile</li>
                <li>Control who can see your posts and achievements</li>
                <li>Manage email communication preferences</li>
                <li>Delete individual posts or comments</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">üç™</span>
              Cookies & Tracking
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>
                We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your
                experience:
              </p>

              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for site
                  functionality and login
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Preference Cookies:</strong> Remember your settings
                  and customizations
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how you
                  use the site
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Social Cookies:</strong> Enable sharing features with
                  other platforms
                </li>
              </ul>

              <p>
                You can control cookie settings through your browser, though
                some features may not work properly if disabled.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">üë•</span>
              Children's Privacy
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>
                The Digital Tavern is designed for adventurers aged 13 and
                older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from
                children under 13.
              </p>

              <p>
                If we discover that we have collected information from a child
                under 13, we will delete it immediately. Parents who believe
                their child has provided us with personal information should
                contact us right away.
              </p>

              <div class="highlight-box">
                <h4>For Young Adventurers (13-17)</h4>
                <p>
                  We encourage parental involvement in your digital adventures.
                  Parents can review their teen's account and request changes or
                  deletion of information.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">üåç</span>
              International Transfers
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>
                Our servers and data may be stored and processed in various
                locations around the world. We ensure appropriate safeguards are
                in place when transferring your information internationally,
                including:
              </p>

              <ul>
                <li>
                  Adequate data protection standards in destination countries
                </li>
                <li>Contractual protections with service providers</li>
                <li>Compliance with applicable international privacy laws</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">
              <span class="section-icon">‚ö°</span>
              Changes to This Policy
            </h2>
            <div class="section-content">
              <p>
                We may update this Privacy Scroll periodically to reflect
                changes in our practices or legal requirements.
              </p>

              <p><strong>When we make changes:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>We'll update the "Last Updated" date at the top</li>
                <li>Significant changes will be announced on our site</li>
                <li>We may send you an email notification for major updates</li>
                <li>
                  Continued use of our services means acceptance of the new
                  terms
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-info">
            <h3>Contact the Tavern Keepers</h3>
            <p>
              Questions about this Privacy Scroll or your personal information?
            </p>
            <p>
              Send a message to:
              <a href="mailto:privacy@digitaltavern.com"
                >privacy@digitaltavern.com</a
              >
            </p>
            <p>
              Postal Address: The Digital Tavern, 123 Adventure Lane, Quest
              City, QC 12345
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Response Time:</strong> We aim to respond within 3-5
              business days
            </p>
          </div>
        </main>

