            <div class="widget-content">
              <p><strong>We protect your privacy by:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Never selling your data</li>
                <li>Using strong encryption</li>
                <li>Giving you control</li>
                <li>Being transparent</li>
                <li>Following the law</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="widget">
            <h3 class="widget-title">Need Help?</h3>
            <div class="widget-content">
              <p>
                Our support team is here to help with any privacy concerns or
